Distributions of the different positions

Multinomial regression analysis

  • Semantic function (11)
  • Morphological structure (ADV, NP, Deict.adv)
  • Positionality (Fillmore 1975)
  • Presence of numerals in the sentence

Increasing P(P1|S1, fi)

  • Around 5 o'clock, During last year, After that,..
  • Numeral present

Decreasing P(P1|S1, fi)

  • Often, every day,…, for five hours, Since 1999…
  • Deictic adverbs
  • Positionality (on Monday, in march, in the morning)
